lines: 3m 610 series is a pressure sensitive sheeting which should be applied at room temperature (15 oc or higher) using a mechanical squeeze roll applicator at moderate pressure

3m reflective sheeting series 610 is an enclosed lens sheeting with a clear pressure sensitive adhesive and easy release liner, intended for production of temporary signs and pressure sensitive stickers which have the same appearance in the daytime and at night when viewed by retroreflected light.
series 610 sheeting has a standard liner and is commonly used for screen printed graphics
3m reflective sheeting 610-10, white, 48 in x 2000 yd, 1 roll/case
